<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="ie=edge">
    <!-- Font Awesome -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://use.fontawesome.com/releases/v5.5.0/css/all.css" integrity="sha384-B4dIYHKNBt8Bc12p+WXckhzcICo0wtJAoU8YZTY5qE0Id1GSseTk6S+L3BlXeVIU" crossorigin="anonymous">

    <!-- Font link -->
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Merriweather|Montserrat" rel="stylesheet">

    <!-- custom css -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/main.css">
    <title>GiftGrab</title>
</head>
<body>
    <%- include('nav', {navClass: ""}); %>

    <!-- showcase image -->
    <section id="showcase" class="d-flex justify-content-center align-items-center">
        <div id="overlay"></div>
        <div id="header" class="container text-center text-white">
            <h1 class="display-1">GiftGrab <i class="fas fa-gift"></i></h1>
            <p class="lead d-none d-lg-block">Gift shopping sucks. <span class="d-block d-sm-inline">Let us do it for you!</span></p>
            <p class="lead d-none d-lg-block">Tell us the item and <span class="d-block d-sm-inline">we'll deliver it to you!</span></p>
            <p class="lead d-lg-none">We gift shop for you!</p>
            <p class="lead d-lg-none">Tell us the item and we'll deliver it!</p>
            <a href="/order"><button id="order" class="btn btn-lg btn-primary p-3">Order Now</button></a>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Opening text -->
    <section id="greeting" class="my-3">
        <div class="container text-center">
            <h1 class="display-3 text-primary">Gift Shop with Ease</h1>
            <hr>
            <p class="lead">Gift shopping is a major pain for the modern man (or woman). Finding the item you're looking for in store takes forever, and waiting in line to checkout feels like an eternity! So let us do the hard work for you!</p>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- 3 column Icon -->
    <section id="threeIcon" class="my-lg-5 text-white bg-primary pt-3">
        <div class="container text-center">
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-lg-4 my-3 my-lg-0">
                    <i class="fas fa-box text-white mb-3"></i>
                    <h3>Gifts on Demand</h3>
                    <p>Tell us what item you want from a local store, and we'll have it to you same day! It's really as easy as that!</p> 
                </div>
                <div class="col-lg-4 my-3 my-lg-0">
                    <i class="fas fa-pause-circle text-white mb-3"></i>
                    <h3>Skip the Wait</h3>
                    <p>Waiting in line sucks...so let one of our grabbers do it for you! This will leave you more time to be with the ones you love...or to play more video games.</p> 
                </div>
                <div class="col-lg-4 my-3 my-lg-0">
                    <i class="fas fa-gift text-white mb-3"></i>
                    <h3>Wrapped with Love</h3>
                    <p>Really strapped on time? GiftGrab has your back! For an additional fee we will wrap all your gifts for you. You get all the credit of course ;)</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Customer section -->
    <section id="customer" class="mt-3 my-lg-5">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-lg-6">
                    <h3 class="text-primary">We Know Our Customers...</h3>
                    <p>We know our customers because we ARE one of our customers!</p>
                    <p>GiftGrab was created by a man who is tired of the hassle of gift shopping and wished there was an easier, and more convienent way!</p>
                    <p>While waiting in line to buy a gift for a friend (wishing he was somewhere else...) an epiphany hit him! "Why not pay someone else to do this for me!?" Thus GiftGrab was born.</p>
                    <button class="btn btn-lg btn-primary">About Us</button>
                </div>
                <div class="col-lg-6 mt-4">
                    <div id="giftgrabCarousel" class="carousel slide" data-ride="carousel">
                        <div class="carousel-inner">
                            <div class="carousel-item active">
                                <img class="d-block w-100" src="../images/christmas.jpg" alt="First slide">
                            </div>
                            <div class="carousel-item">
                                <img class="d-block w-100" src="../images/valentines.jpg" alt="Second slide">
                            </div>
                            <div class="carousel-item">
                                <img class="d-block w-100" src="../images/birthday.jpg" alt="Third slide">
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <a class="carousel-control-prev" href="#giftgrabCarousel" role="button" data-slide="prev">
                            <span class="carousel-control-prev-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
                            <span class="sr-only">Previous</span>
                        </a>
                        <a class="carousel-control-next" href="#giftgrabCarousel" role="button" data-slide="next">
                            <span class="carousel-control-next-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
                            <span class="sr-only">Next</span>
                        </a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Meet the Team -->
    <section id="team" class="bg-primary mt-5 py-3 text-center">
        <div class="container">
            <h1 class="display-3 text-white">Meet the Team</h1>
            <hr>
            <div class="row">
                    <div class="col-md-6 offset-md-3">
                            <div class="card">
                                    <img class="card-img-top" src="../images/ryanweb.jpg" alt="Card image cap">
                                    <div class="card-body">
                                      <h5 class="card-title text-primary">Ryan Talbert</h5>
                                      <p class="card-text">Ryan is an internet entrepreneur who founded GiftGrab! He own's 2 companies and will most likely be the one bringing you your gifts!</p>
                                      <a href="#" class="btn btn-outline-primary">See Profile</a>
                                    </div>
                                  </div>        
                    </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- quotes -->
    <section id="quotes">
        <div class="container text-center">
            <h1 class="display-3 text-primary mt-3 mt-lg-0 mb-md-3">What our customers say:</h1>
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-lg-4">
                    <i class="fas fa-quote-left fa-2x text-primary mb-2 mt-3 mt-lg-0"></i>
                    <blockquote class="blockquote">
                        <p class="mb-0">GiftGrab has saved me so much time gift shopping this holiday season! I LOVE them!</p>
                        <footer class="blockquote-footer">Alison Seibel</footer>
                    </blockquote>
                </div>
                <div class="col-lg-4">
                        <i class="fas fa-quote-left fa-2x text-primary mb-2 mt-3 mt-lg-0"></i>
                        <blockquote class="blockquote">
                            <p class="mb-0">It's nice not having to worry about getting all my shopping done this holiday season. I can finally relax and enjoy time with my family.</p>
                            <footer class="blockquote-footer">Vita Genna</footer>
                        </blockquote>
                    </div>
                <div class="col-lg-4">
                    <i class="fas fa-quote-left fa-2x text-primary mb-2 mt-3 mt-lg-0"></i>
                    <blockquote class="blockquote">
                        <p class="mb-0">I literally hate gift shopping. I am so glad there is a company that will do it for me!</p>
                        <footer class="blockquote-footer">Clark Atwood</footer>
                    </blockquote>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- 2 column section -->
    <section id="pricing" class="my-3 d-flex bg-primary text-white py-3">
        <div class="container text-center">
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-lg-8">
                    <h3 id="pricingHeader">Our Pricing</h3>
                    <div class="row">
                            <div class="col-lg-6 my-3 my-lg-0">
                                    <h3 class="">Service Charge</h3>
                                    <h5 class="">20%</h5>
                                    <p>GiftGrab charges a $10 service fee for all purchases under $50, and a 20% service fee for all purchases over $50.</p>
                                </div>
                                <div class="col-lg-6 my-3 my-lg-0">
                                    <h3 class="">Gift Wrapping</h3>
                                    <h5 class="">$5 / <i class="fas fa-gift"></i></h5>
                                    <p>GiftGrab charges $5 per gift that you need wrapped.</p>
                                </div>
                    </div>
                    <a href="order.html"><button class="btn btn-lg btn-light text-primary d-none d-lg-inline">Order Now</button></a>
                </div>
                <div class="col-lg-4 my-3 my-lg-0">
                    <h3 class="">Areas we Serve:</h3>
                    <div id="cities" class="d-flex flex-column justify-content-lg-center align-self-lg-center">
                        <span class="city ">Ballwin, MO</span>
                        <span class="city ">Manchester, MO</span>
                    </div>
                    <a href="/order"><button class="btn btn-lg btn-light text-primary d-inline d-lg-none mt-5">Order Now</button></a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
    
    <!-- social media -->
    <section id="social" class="pb-5">
        <div class="container text-center">
                <h1 class="display-3 text-primary mb-4">Connect with Us</h1>
                <div class="d-flex justify-content-between">
                    <a href="https://www.facebook.com"><i class="fab fa-facebook-square text-primary"></i></a>
                    <a href="https://www.instagram.com"><i class="fab fa-instagram text-primary"></i></a>
                    <a href="https://www.twitter.com"><i class="fab fa-twitter-square text-primary"></i></a>
                </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- footer -->
  <footer id="footer" class="bg-primary text-white py-3">
        <div class="container">
          <div class="row text-center">
            <div class="col-md-6">
              <h3><i class="fas fa-gift"></i> GiftGrab</h3>
              <hr class="light">
              <p>636-484-2273</p>
              <p>klaurtar@gmail.com</p>
              <p>710 La Marite Dr.</p>
              <p>Manchester, MO, 63021</p>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-6">
              <h3>Our Hours</h3>
              <hr class="light">
              <p>Monday-Friday: 9am to 5pm</p>
              <p>Saturday: 9am to 5pm</p>
              <p>Sunday: 9am to 5pm</p>
            </div>
            <div class="col-12">
              <hr class="light">
              <h5>&copy; GiftGrab.com <span id="year"></span></h5>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </footer>



